{"tid":2254281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★瑞信報告顯示新冠疫情 中國家庭變得更加富裕","createTime":"2020-10-22T16:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T17:01:35.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e99f5667f6867524ba5d9a2ba981a70d66853ca3","tid":2254281,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T16:43:42.000Z","msg":"【彭博】-- 導致全球超過100萬人死亡的新冠疫情還導致個人財富減少，但中國和印度的家庭財富在很大程度上得到維持甚至增加。<br />\n<br />\n中國和印度家庭財富增加<br />\n<br />\n上半年，只有中國和印度的家庭財富有所成長，分別成長了4.4%和1.6%。拉丁美洲遭受的損失最大，暴跌了13%，原因是貨幣貶值加劇了國內生產毛額的損失。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E7%91%9E%E4%BF%A1%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E6%8B%96%E7%B4%AF%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%A1%E5%AF%8C-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E8%AE%8A%E5%BE%97%E6%9B%B4%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%8C%E8%A3%95-144404203.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E7%2591%259E%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%258B%2596%25E7%25B4%25AF%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E5%25AF%258C-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%25BE%2597%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25AF%258C%25E8%25A3%2595-144404203.html&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FREx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=51d044cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E7%91%9E%E4%BF%A1%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E6%8B%96%E7%B4%AF%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%A1%E5%AF%8C-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E8%AE%8A%E5%BE%97%E6%9B%B4%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%8C%E8%A3%95-144404203.html</a>"},{"pid":"2366c466f2c18c87cf7378cc23f0d3ed71f142e2","tid":2254281,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T16:44:00.000Z","msg":"more virus<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass